This is a cover of *ELLE België* magazine, featuring Chiara Ferragni. She wears a stylish pale pink suit with a deep neckline, accessorized with layered gold necklaces, bracelets, and rings. Her wavy blonde hair frames her face as she looks confidently into the camera, complemented by bold red lipstick and subtle makeup. The cover emphasizes themes of "Girl Power" in bold black text and includes interviews and features on fashion, trends, and notable personalities like the Jonas Brothers and Dua Lipa. The layout combines modern typography and minimalist design, highlighting empowerment and style.

This is the cover of *Elle België* magazine from October 2019. The focus is on "Girl Power," with the featured individual wearing a stylish pink suit with a deep neckline. The text highlights Chiara Ferragni, known as an influential fashion blogger, with her quote “Ik ben geen slaaf van sociale media” ("I am not a slave to social media"). Other features include interviews with Ann Demeulemeester, the Jonas Brothers, Dua Lipa, and others. Accessories include delicate necklaces, rings, and bracelets. The cover emphasizes winter shopping trends, empowering themes, and exclusive features.
